   Wednesday's Markets:
   Dollar Posts
   Steep Drop,
   Bonds Fall
   ---
   Stocks, in Response,
   End Mixed as Streak
   Of Gains Is Halted
   ----
   By Douglas R. Sease
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
